{"tid":2002685,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署：個別人士不滿服刑待遇可投訴","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T14:43:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa92bc83a73da06fb543694db7e177c7fe15dba","tid":2002685,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"狗隊叫黨衛軍<br />\n懲教署應該叫咩 ?<br />\n<br />\n懲教署：個別人士不滿服刑待遇可投訴<br />\n05.05.2020 18:18<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志舉行記者會，指控懲教人員暴力對待反修例人士。眾志秘書長黃之鋒指，收到幾名早前還押、目前已保釋的人士求助，指2月在壁屋懲教所時，唱出反修例歌曲，幾日後他們被一名職員掌摑，亦被命令自摑，批評是酷刑對待。懲教署回覆指，如果個別人士不滿服刑期間的待遇，可向署方投訴，將按既定機制處理，並建議有關人士聯絡署方提供資料，以便跟進。<br />\n<br />\n社福界立法會議員邵家臻指，早前探望囚友時已聽聞事件，但當時因他們仍在還押，所以不敢揭發。他指，反修例人士在獄中被懲教人員稱呼為「暴動仔」，他們不時都會唱歌解悶。他要求懲教署長胡英明交代今次事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285331&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285331%26csid%3D261_341&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktbYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=be7b542b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285331&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f4f80cf65e1f93ce4b32a657d078d6f7a209da84","tid":2002685,"uid":13343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"黑甲由： 搵投訴科"},{"pid":"67cc72a7ca81884e51fa577c0826461a08b5e44d","tid":2002685,"uid":259716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"DLLM既定機制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cb7311a714bb3923eb00704a3465aeb85ae961","tid":2002685,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"懲教狗有冇槍?"},{"pid":"bb106e46b32f0061610d5529b7ea13856cf7ed3f","tid":2002685,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4ec473d7085959670fcd623e2bbd44b06286408","